$interpreted: Furygrowl: Dammit! Let's see you block this!
Dagger: Furygrowl!!
Dagger: Enough already, get out of the way!
Dagger: Great shot!!
Naya: Thanks~
Naya: Hey, can you get up?
Furygrowl: Just... about...
Golemwalt: Gruuuu~~~
Dagger: Golemwalt!? You're still alive!?
Golemwalt: Gruuu~
Nolva: Are you... Dagger?
Nolva: Hey, is this Totemtaff? There's monsters all over the place!
Dagger: Good timing, you can fill in for Furygrowl! You good, Golemwalt?
Golemwalt: Gruuu!
Dagger: They just keep on comin'!
Naya: At this rate we'll soon be worn ragged!
Crushfang: Withdraw!
Dagger: But it ain't over just yet...!
Crushfang: Look around you. It's long over already, you'd just rather not admit it.
Dagger: ......
Crushfang: ...Pack it in, both of you. We'll live to fight another day!
Dagger: All right, all right~ I get it, you're happy. Stop that, you're real heavy!
Naya: I'm Naya Rosset. I've come to Totemtaff by order of my Queen to request their assistance.
Naya: You said you've come from Paradise Prairie on an SOS call?
Nolva: Yes... But I got a little lost on the way. Luckily this Golem was here to show me the way...
Dagger: That's Golemwalt. We lost so many Golems the night Totemtaff was raided.
Dagger: I thought that you were...
Golemwalt: Gruu~
Dagger: Ahh all right, enough already! You're gonna make me cry, get your paws off me.
Naya: Haha, you two make a good team.
Nolva: ...I'm sorry, I don't understand...
Naya: To put it simply, the Bears are also in a spot of trouble. You saw all those monsters outside, right?
Nolva: But how...
Dagger: The Chieftain already promised help after we received Angelia's message. But just as we were about to set out, Totemtaff was ambushed...
Naya: I got caught in the middle of it all. I haven't been able to get back to report to the Queen.
Naya: We've been trying to break the onslaught, but every attempt's failed, like the one you just witnessed.
Dagger: This can't go on much longer. Totemtaff will starve if we don't settle this soon!
Naya: ...Crushfang's right, though. With so many monsters out there, all our efforts so far have been futile...
Dagger: I'll take futility over fatality any day! I'm gonna go talk him around!!
Naya: Dagger, wait! I'm coming too!
Nolva: (...It was such a slog just getting to Totemtaff... but else what can I do now...)
Nolva: (Whaa? A-Again!?)
Nolva: (...It's stopped!)
Nolva: (I-I can't hear anything anymore...)
Naya: I'm sorry, I almost forgot about you. Do you wanna come with...
Naya: Are you okay? Did something happen?
Nolva: That sound! Did you hear somebody speaking a moment ago!?
Naya: Somebody speaking?
Naya: Nope, I didn't hear a thing. I haven't seen anyone here, besides you and me.
Nolva: But I heard something...! It was so loud...
